Tamara Geva https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamara_Geva 0 Tamara Geva (Russian: Тамара Гева, Жева, or Жева; 17 March 1907 – 9 December 1997) was a Russian-American actress, ballet dancer and choreographer. She was the first wife of dancer/choreographer George Balanchine.
